7857template<typename E>
7858std::shared_ptr<types::IExtension> WrapExtension(
7859 const std::shared_ptr<types::IExtension>& that,
7860 const std::function<
7861 std::shared_ptr<E>(
7862 const std::shared_ptr<types::IClass>&
7863 )
7864 >& factory
7865) {
7866 // We assume that we already checked whether `that` has been enhanced
7867 // in the caller.
7868
7869 if (that->semantic_id().has_value()) {
7870 const std::shared_ptr<types::IReference>& value(
7871 that->semantic_id().value()
7872 );
7873
7874 std::shared_ptr<
7875 types::IReference
7876 > wrapped(
7877 Wrap<E>(
7878 value,
7879 factory
7880 )
7881 );
7882
7883 that->set_semantic_id(
7884 common::make_optional(
7885 std::move(wrapped)
7886 )
7887 );
7888 }
7889
7890 if (that->supplemental_semantic_ids().has_value()) {
7891 const std::vector<
7892 std::shared_ptr<types::IReference>
7893 >& value(
7894 that->supplemental_semantic_ids().value()
7895 );
7896 const std::size_t size = value.size();
7897
7898 std::vector<
7899 std::shared_ptr<types::IReference>
7900 > wrapped;
7901 wrapped.reserve(size);
7902
7903 for (
7904 const std::shared_ptr<types::IReference>& item
7905 : value
7906 ) {
7907 wrapped.emplace_back(
7908 Wrap<E>(
7909 item,
7910 factory
7911 )
7912 );
7913 }
7914
7915 that->set_supplemental_semantic_ids(
7916 common::make_optional(
7917 std::move(wrapped)
7918 )
7919 );
7920 }
7921
7922 if (that->refers_to().has_value()) {
7923 const std::vector<
7924 std::shared_ptr<types::IReference>
7925 >& value(
7926 that->refers_to().value()
7927 );
7928 const std::size_t size = value.size();
7929
7930 std::vector<
7931 std::shared_ptr<types::IReference>
7932 > wrapped;
7933 wrapped.reserve(size);
7934
7935 for (
7936 const std::shared_ptr<types::IReference>& item
7937 : value
7938 ) {
7939 wrapped.emplace_back(
7940 Wrap<E>(
7941 item,
7942 factory
7943 )
7944 );
7945 }
7946
7947 that->set_refers_to(
7948 common::make_optional(
7949 std::move(wrapped)
7950 )
7951 );
7952 }
7953
7954 std::shared_ptr<E> enh(
7955 factory(that)
7956 );
7957 return (enh == nullptr)
7958 ? that
7959 : std::shared_ptr<types::IExtension>(
7960 new EnhancedExtension<E>(
7961 that,
7962 enh
7963 )
7964 );
7965}
7966
7976template<typename E>
7977std::shared_ptr<types::IAdministrativeInformation> WrapAdministrativeInformation(
7978 const std::shared_ptr<types::IAdministrativeInformation>& that,
7979 const std::function<
7980 std::shared_ptr<E>(
7981 const std::shared_ptr<types::IClass>&
7982 )
7983 >& factory
7984) {
7985 // We assume that we already checked whether `that` has been enhanced
7986 // in the caller.
7987
7988 if (that->embedded_data_specifications().has_value()) {
7989 const std::vector<
7990 std::shared_ptr<types::IEmbeddedDataSpecification>
7991 >& value(
7992 that->embedded_data_specifications().value()
7993 );
7994 const std::size_t size = value.size();
7995
7996 std::vector<
7997 std::shared_ptr<types::IEmbeddedDataSpecification>
7998 > wrapped;
7999 wrapped.reserve(size);
8000
8001 for (
8002 const std::shared_ptr<types::IEmbeddedDataSpecification>& item
8003 : value
8004 ) {
8005 wrapped.emplace_back(
8006 Wrap<E>(
8007 item,
8008 factory
8009 )
8010 );
8011 }
8012
8013 that->set_embedded_data_specifications(
8014 common::make_optional(
8015 std::move(wrapped)
8016 )
8017 );
8018 }
8019
8020 if (that->creator().has_value()) {
8021 const std::shared_ptr<types::IReference>& value(
8022 that->creator().value()
8023 );
8024
8025 std::shared_ptr<
8026 types::IReference
8027 > wrapped(
8028 Wrap<E>(
8029 value,
8030 factory
8031 )
8032 );
8033
8034 that->set_creator(
8035 common::make_optional(
8036 std::move(wrapped)
8037 )
8038 );
8039 }
8040
8041 std::shared_ptr<E> enh(
8042 factory(that)
8043 );
8044 return (enh == nullptr)
8045 ? that
8046 : std::shared_ptr<types::IAdministrativeInformation>(
8047 new EnhancedAdministrativeInformation<E>(
8048 that,
8049 enh
8050 )

9112 const std::size_t size = value.size();
9113
9114 std::vector<
9115 std::shared_ptr<types::IQualifier>

9119 for (
9120 const std::shared_ptr<types::IQualifier>& item
9121 : value
9122 ) {

9124 Wrap<E>(
9125 item,
9126 factory
9127 )
9128 );
9129 }

9131 that->set_qualifiers(
9132 common::make_optional(
9133 std::move(wrapped)
9134 )
9135 );
9136 }
9137
9138 if (that->embedded_data_specifications().has_value()) {
9139 const std::vector<
9140 std::shared_ptr<types::IEmbeddedDataSpecification>
9141 >& value(
9142 that->embedded_data_specifications().value()
9143 );
9144 const std::size_t size = value.size();
9145
9146 std::vector<
9147 std::shared_ptr<types::IEmbeddedDataSpecification>

9157 item,
9158 factory
9159 )

9164 common::make_optional(
9165 std::move(wrapped)
9166 )
9167 );
9168 }
9169
9170 that->set_first(
9171 Wrap<E>(
9172 that->first(),
9173 factory
9174 )
9175 );
9176
9177 that->set_second(
9178 Wrap<E>(
9179 that->second(),
9180 factory
9181 )
9182 );
9183
9184 std::shared_ptr<E> enh(
9185 factory(that)
9186 );

9188 ? that

9190 new EnhancedRelationshipElement<E>(

9192 enh
9193 )
9194 );

14013
14022template<
14023 typename E,
14024 typename T,
14025 typename std::enable_if<
14026 std::is_base_of<types::IClass, T>::value
14027 >::type* = nullptr
14028>
14029void AssertNotEnhanced(
14030 const std::shared_ptr<T>& that
14031) {
14032 std::shared_ptr<impl::IEnhanced<E> > enhanced(
14033 std::dynamic_pointer_cast<
14034 impl::IEnhanced<E>
14035 >(that)
14036 );
14037 if (enhanced != nullptr) {
14038 throw std::logic_error(
14039 common::Concat(
14040 "An instance of ",
14041 stringification::to_string(that->model_type()),
14042 " has been already wrapped."
14043 )
14044 );
14045 }
14046}
14047
14048} // namespace impl
14050
14066
14067template <typename E>
14068std::shared_ptr<
14069 types::IClass
14070> Wrap(
14071 const std::shared_ptr<
14072 types::IClass
14073 >& that,
14074 const std::function<
14075 std::shared_ptr<E>(
14076 const std::shared_ptr<types::IClass>&
14077 )
14078 >& factory
14079) {
14080 impl::AssertNotEnhanced<
14081 E,
14082 types::IClass
14083 >(that);
14084
14085 switch (that->model_type()) {
14086 case types::ModelType::kExtension:
14087 return impl::WrapExtension<E>(
14088 std::dynamic_pointer_cast<
14089 types::IExtension
14090 >(that),
14091 factory
14092 );
14093 break;
14094 case types::ModelType::kAdministrativeInformation:
14095 return impl::WrapAdministrativeInformation<E>(
14096 std::dynamic_pointer_cast<
14097 types::IAdministrativeInformation

17278template <typename E>
17279std::shared_ptr<E> Unwrap(
17280 const std::shared_ptr<types::IClass>& that
17281) {
17282 const std::shared_ptr<impl::IEnhanced<E> >& maybe_enhanced(
17283 std::dynamic_pointer_cast<impl::IEnhanced<E> >(that)
17284 );
17285
17286 if (!maybe_enhanced) {
17287 return nullptr;
17288 }
17289
17290 return maybe_enhanced->enhancement();
17291}
17292
17303template <typename E>
17304std::shared_ptr<E> MustUnwrap(
17305 const std::shared_ptr<types::IClass>& that
17306) {
17307 std::shared_ptr<E> enhancement(
17308 Unwrap<E>(that)
17309 );
17310 if (!enhancement) {
17311 throw std::invalid_argument(
17312 common::Concat(
17313 "Expected an instance of ",
17314 stringification::to_string(that->model_type()),
17315 " to have been already wrapped with an enhancement, "
17316 "but it has been not."
17317 )
17318 );
17319 }
17320 return enhancement;
17321}
